  <!-- §2 · HOW WE HANDLE YOUR DATA -->
  <section id="data" class="w-section cz-light sec-block w-panel-rise" data-nav-surface="light">
    <div class="w-container">
      <div class="w-section-head w-reveal">
        <span class="sec-eyebrow"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-shield"/></svg>Data protection</span>
        <h2 class="w-section-head__title">Your data is protected in transit, at rest, <span class="w-accent">and in use.</span></h2>
        <p class="w-section-head__lead">SlashExperts handles two kinds of sensitive data — your prospects' and buyers' contact and conversation data, and your customers' participation data. Both are handled so that only authorized systems and people can read them, access is restricted on a least-privilege basis, and we collect only what the product needs to do its job.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sec-grid sec-grid--three w-stagger">
        <div class="w-card w-card--brand sec-card w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
          <span class="w-card__icon"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-link"/></svg></span>
          <h3 class="w-card__title">Encryption in transit</h3>
          <p class="w-card__body">All traffic is secured with TLS 1.2+.</p>
          <div class="w-card__foot"><span class="sec-tag"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-shield"/></svg>TLS enforced</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-card w-card--brand sec-card w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
          <span class="w-card__icon"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-shield"/></svg></span>
          <h3 class="w-card__title">Encryption at rest</h3>
          <p class="w-card__body">Stored data is encrypted at rest using AES-256.</p>
          <div class="w-card__foot"><span class="sec-tag"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-shield"/></svg>AES-256</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-card w-card--brand sec-card w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
          <span class="w-card__icon"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-widget"/></svg></span>
          <h3 class="w-card__title">Hosting &amp; infrastructure</h3>
          <p class="w-card__body">Hosted in the United States on AWS, with Standard Contractual Clauses for international transfers.</p>
          <div class="w-card__foot"><span class="sec-tag"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-shield"/></svg>US · AWS</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-card w-card--brand sec-card w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
          <span class="w-card__icon"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-users"/></svg></span>
          <h3 class="w-card__title">Access control</h3>
          <p class="w-card__body">Internal access follows least-privilege, restricted to authorized systems and people.</p>
          <div class="w-card__foot"><span class="sec-tag"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-shield"/></svg>Least-privilege</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-card w-card--brand sec-card w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
          <span class="w-card__icon"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-file"/></svg></span>
          <h3 class="w-card__title">Data minimization &amp; retention</h3>
          <p class="w-card__body">We keep data only as long as the service requires, and remove personal data on deletion request.</p>
          <div class="w-card__foot"><span class="sec-tag"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-shield"/></svg>Policy in place</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="sec-close-line w-reveal">Where you need the full detail, our security package includes our data-flow diagram and sub-processor list.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- §3 · PRIVACY & YOUR CUSTOMERS' RIGHTS -->
  <section id="privacy" class="w-section cz-light sec-block" data-nav-surface="light">
    <div class="w-container">
      <div class="w-section-head w-reveal">
        <span class="sec-eyebrow"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-users"/></svg>Privacy</span>
        <h2 class="w-section-head__title">Built to respect the people <span class="w-accent">whose proof you share.</span></h2>
        <p class="w-section-head__lead">A Trust Layer only works if the customers in it are treated well and the buyers it reaches are handled lawfully. Everyone in the network participates by opt-in, controls their own participation, and can withdraw at any time; every booking and conversation happens with the participant's knowledge. We process personal data on your behalf, under a Data Processing Agreement.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sec-grid sec-grid--three w-stagger">
        <div class="w-card w-card--brand sec-card w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
          <span class="w-card__icon"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-shield"/></svg></span>
          <h3 class="w-card__title">GDPR</h3>
          <p class="w-card__body">Full compliance with the EU GDPR — data subject rights, lawful processing, and cross-border transfer protections. <a class="sec-inline-link" href="/gdpr">Read our GDPR statement</a>.</p>
          <div class="w-card__foot"><span class="sec-tag"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-shield"/></svg>Compliant</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-card w-card--brand sec-card w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
          <span class="w-card__icon"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-scan"/></svg></span>
          <h3 class="w-card__title">CCPA</h3>
          <p class="w-card__body">California residents have full control over their personal information, including opt-out and deletion rights. <a class="sec-inline-link" href="/ccpa">See our CCPA notice</a>.</p>
          <div class="w-card__foot"><span class="sec-tag"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-shield"/></svg>Ready</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-card w-card--brand sec-card w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
          <span class="w-card__icon"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-file"/></svg></span>
          <h3 class="w-card__title">Data subject requests</h3>
          <p class="w-card__body">Access, correction, and deletion requests are handled per our privacy documentation.</p>
          <div class="w-card__foot"><span class="sec-tag"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-shield"/></svg>Supported</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-card w-card--brand sec-card w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
          <span class="w-card__icon"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-link"/></svg></span>
          <h3 class="w-card__title">Sub-processors</h3>
          <p class="w-card__body">Current sub-processors include AWS and Salesforce; subscribe to change notifications by email.</p>
          <div class="w-card__foot"><span class="sec-tag"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-shield"/></svg>In our DPA</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-card w-card--brand sec-card w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
          <span class="w-card__icon"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-widget"/></svg></span>
          <h3 class="w-card__title">Data residency</h3>
          <p class="w-card__body">Your data is hosted in the United States.</p>
          <div class="w-card__foot"><span class="sec-tag"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-shield"/></svg>US-hosted</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="sec-close-line w-reveal">Our <a class="sec-inline-link" href="/dpa">DPA</a> and sub-processor list, and our <a class="sec-inline-link" href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>, are available in full.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- §4 · THE INTEGRITY OF EVERY EXPERT -->
  <section id="integrity" class="w-section sec-sign w-panel-rise--dark" data-nav-surface="dark">
    <div class="w-container">
      <div class="w-section-head w-reveal">
        <span class="w-badge"><span class="w-badge__icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#i-match"/></svg></span>The signature standard</span>
        <h2 class="sec-sign__h">Real proof starts with <span class="w-accent">a real customer.</span></h2>
        <p class="sec-sign__lead">The whole point of a Trust Layer is that a buyer hears from someone who has genuinely done what they're about to do. So verification isn't a feature here — it's the foundation. Every expert in the network is a real, verified customer, not an anonymous reviewer or a paid stand-in. We confirm who they are and that their experience is real before they ever appear in front of a buyer, and every conversation is on the record in your CRM.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sec-flow w-stagger" role="list" aria-label="Verification flow">
        <span class="sec-flow__node w-reveal w-reveal--scale" role="listitem"><span class="sec-flow__ic"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-users"/></svg></span><b>Real customer</b></span>
