        <span class="sec-flow__node w-reveal w-reveal--scale" role="listitem"><span class="sec-flow__ic"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span><b>Consented</b></span>
        <span class="sec-flow__link" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sec-flow__node w-reveal w-reveal--scale" role="listitem"><span class="sec-flow__ic"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-scan"/></svg></span><b>On the record</b></span>
      </div>
      <div class="sec-grid w-stagger">
        <div class="w-card w-card--brand sec-card w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
          <span class="w-card__icon"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-shield"/></svg></span>
          <h3 class="w-card__title">Identity &amp; customer status</h3>
          <p class="w-card__body">Each expert is verified as a genuine customer before they appear.</p>
          <div class="w-card__foot"><span class="sec-tag sec-tag--pending"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-clock"/></svg>Pending: verification mechanism</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-card w-card--brand sec-card w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
          <span class="w-card__icon"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>
          <h3 class="w-card__title">Consent &amp; participation</h3>
          <p class="w-card__body">Experts opt in explicitly and control their availability, topics, and when they step out.</p>
          <div class="w-card__foot"><span class="sec-tag sec-tag--pending"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-clock"/></svg>Pending: participation controls</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-card w-card--feature sec-card w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
          <span class="w-card__icon"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-scan"/></svg></span>
          <h3 class="w-card__title">On the record</h3>
          <p class="w-card__body">Every match, booking, and outcome is logged to your CRM, so the provenance of every proof point is auditable — never an unattributable claim.</p>
          <div class="w-card__foot"><span class="sec-tag"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-shield"/></svg>Logged to CRM</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-card w-card--brand sec-card w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
          <span class="w-card__icon"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-star"/></svg></span>
          <h3 class="w-card__title">Compensation transparency</h3>
          <p class="w-card__body">Where experts are compensated, it's disclosed and structured so it never trades for a scripted opinion.</p>
          <div class="w-card__foot"><span class="sec-tag sec-tag--pending"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-clock"/></svg>Pending: compensation / disclosure policy</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="sec-sign__close w-reveal">This is the security story that matters most for a trust product: <span class="w-accent">the proof your buyers act on is real because the customer behind it is real, verified, and accountable.</span></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- §5 · HOW THE CRM CONNECTION IS SECURED -->
  <section id="crm" class="w-section cz-light sec-block w-panel-rise" data-nav-surface="light">
    <div class="w-container">
      <div class="w-section-head w-reveal">
        <span class="sec-eyebrow"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-link"/></svg>CRM connection</span>
