        <p class="w-section-head__lead">SlashExperts syncs with your CRM so every booking and outcome lands on the record. That connection is built to take only the access it needs and to write only what you authorize. You stay in control of the scopes you grant, and you can revoke the connection at any time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sec-grid w-stagger">
        <div class="w-card w-card--brand sec-card w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
