          <h3 class="w-card__title">Least-privilege writes</h3>
          <p class="w-card__body">SlashExperts writes only to the objects and fields you authorize.</p>
          <div class="w-card__foot"><span class="sec-tag"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-shield"/></svg>You control scope</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-card w-card--brand sec-card w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
          <span class="w-card__icon"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-settings"/></svg></span>
