        <div class="w-card w-card--brand sec-card w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
          <span class="w-card__icon"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-link"/></svg></span>
          <h3 class="w-card__title">Supported platforms</h3>
          <p class="w-card__body">Works with Salesforce, HubSpot, and the tools your team already runs on. See <a class="sec-inline-link" href="/integrations">Integrations</a> for the full list.</p>
          <div class="w-card__foot"><span class="sec-tag"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-shield"/></svg>Salesforce · HubSpot</span></div>
        </div>
